title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: The real value in any gift is if its seen as a mere reflection of your care and character. However, you may believe that you need to prove your worth to someone special today. You might even try to make a positive impression through an extravagant gesture. Nevertheless, you wont likely earn the adoration you are seeking if the object of your affection doesn't already appreciate you. Trust that this person is judging you from your presence in their life and not your desire to spoil them with material goods. Friendship is a priceless treasure never to be bought or sold -- it can only be cherished. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
